    // ── About page ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
    'about.statement':        'Communicating well<br>is a matter of choices.<br><em>Every mark counts.</em>',
    'about.title':            'About me',
    'about.body':             '<p>I\'m a <strong>Graphic Designer</strong> based in Brescia. I started out with a diploma in <strong>Green Product Design</strong> at ITS Academy Machina Lonati. Then visual communication drew me in: the way a mark, a colour, a typographic choice can shift how people perceive things.</p><p>Over the past few years I\'ve worked with several agencies, building visual identities and online and offline communication for very different clients. Every project starts from the same question: what does it need to say, and to whom?</p><p>Since September 2025 I\'m also a <strong>Design student at the Free University of Bolzano</strong>. I study while I work, because I believe learning never really stops.</p>',
    'about.skills.label':     'Expertise',
